	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Mon, Apr 8th 6:18 AM 2002</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=145143><span id=Scholar>wolas</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>28 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Another trick with harmony. <br><br>Sometimes you cant harmony creatures on top of something (like aviaks in SK or spectres in oasis) because it says you you are too far aways.<br><br>In this case just go close under the mobs, target yourself and cast harmony on you. The mobs upstairs will all be harmonized. <br><br>Good pulling...<br><br>--------------<br>Wolas<br>44 Wood elf Druid<br>Antonious Bayle</p>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
