	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=73409><span id=Scholar>Mistress ancarett</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>108 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default [2.30]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>Do NOT put any of your points into intelligence. Intelligence is used by INT casters including: Necromancer, Wizard, Magician and Enchanter (also the hybrid Shadow Knight).<br><br>Druids are WIS casters, along with Clerics, Shamans (also hybrids Beastlords and Paladins).&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </p>&nbsp;<br>-- Ancarett, who lives at <a href="http://ancarett.com" target=_new>http://ancarett.com</a></td></tr>
